   <h2>1A2B</h2>
   <h4>Game Rule</h4>
   <Div class="centerDiv">
   <p>Please enter the different three numbers between 0 and 9, don't repeat.<br>3A wins the game<br><br>A → The guess number is the same as random number and the position is  same.<br>B → The guess number is the same as random number,but in the different position.</p>
      <p>Ex:<br>random numer:216<br>Guess number:241<br>1A1B : 2 is A. 1 is B.</p>
